OL,3,GSouth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRain or
OL,6,Fshowers this evening but turning drier
OL,7,Ffrom the west overnight with clear
OL,8,Fspells. Showers possible in west
OL,9,FCornwall by dawn. Windy in the
OL,10,Fsouthwest to start, before easing.
OL,11,FTurning chilly in the countryside with
OL,12,Fisolated fog patches.
OL,13,
OL,14,CSaturday:FDry for many with sunny
OL,15,Fperiods and feeling fairly pleasant
OL,16,Fwith light winds. Isolated showers may
OL,17,Fgraze western coasts before heavier
OL,18,Fshowers push eastwards during the
OL,19,Fevening. Freshening winds later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
